data.description: Check out this adorable home, freshly updated! 2 stories with owner suite and 1.5 half bathrooms downstairs. Cozy up by the fire place in this generously sized living room with soaring ceilings! New floors, fresh paint, new hot water heater, new vanity in owner suite, new closet doors, all new lighting, roof 2 years old, ac 2 years old, new bathtub insert in upstairs bathroom! Located on a cul de' sac in a sought after Sugarmill neighborhood in St. Marys HOA includes pool, tennis courts and playground!!
